  "title": "BIM Modeller",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Prepare detailed architectural and structural shop drawings and working drawings using Revit, ensuring all designs comply with project construction requirements.</li>\n  <li>Provide timely BIM coordination support to the Project Team, delivering accurate information to facilitate construction activities.</li>\n  <li>Extract data from 3D Revit models to produce shop drawings, resolving any discrepancies in collaboration with the Engineering Department and Project Team.</li>\n  <li>Develop detailed drawings and specifications in accordance with client and consultant requirements.</li>\n  <li>Produce as-built drawings for submission and handover upon project completion.</li>\n  <li>Assist in tender bids and drawing preparation, including the development of overall floor plans and sectional drawings.</li>\n  <li>Attend technical and BIM meetings as required.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all required drawings are completed accurately and within scheduled deadlines.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981| EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
